[Scene01]

Emerging from the flooded tunnel Bob and Teeka were greeted by the early morning sun and the 
sounds of battle. They had arrived just in the nick of time to help drive off the attacking 
BioMech forces. However they would still need to hurry in order to save their fellow Blobs from destruction.

[Scene02]

It was likely that there would be many wounded Blobs and possibly prisoners. Bob would need to 
find some medicine and save the prisoners from the threat of assimilation. Drawing close to the
exit of the tunnel Bob could make out the sound of sentry cannons bombarding his home base.
The enemy had certainly been busy in his absence...

[END]
